{
  "stem": "4345.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And all this-- and I saw two women were holding mommy up, because she could not see anymore what she's doing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was all covered with blood.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they helped her up on the steps to the train.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you know, they could not close the doors.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because the people-- you know, it was too, too much.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they use the rope, they shouldn't fall out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I don't know if Mommy saw us, but I didn't see her either.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She must have been laying there [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then when-- then we went home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When we came home, we told Daddy-- Daddy asked us, where's Mommy?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had to tell him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As soon as we told him what happened to Mommy, he fell to the floor.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he, he became paralyzed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A total paralysis came over him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It, it was like he was stricken with some kind of a muscular dystrophy or something.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He couldn't move.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He couldn't-- he was totally, like, you know, like doubled up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I couldn't call a doctor.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because if I call a doctor, they would not come and help.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They would-- to a hospital, they wouldn't take him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then they would send the German.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And maybe the Polack alone himself will kill him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So we kept him home for as long as we were together.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After that, I went to work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is where I'm going back, when I went to work the [?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Trebinje ?], and should I repeat all that?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was-- and our, our IDs were taken from us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, and my sister told me not to go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I did go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they killed those poor kids behind the building.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then we walked from [?",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
